commentAnnotations.text: Janssen Research & Development is a global organization that operates through different legal entities in various countries. The term 'sponsor' is used to represent these various legal entities.

Stable remission: MADRS total score â‰¤12 for at least 3 of the last 4 weeks of the optimization phase, but one excursion >12 or one missing assessment is permitted at Optimization week 13 or 14 only.
Benzodiazepine rescue medication is permitted only post-dose on the dosing day.
At the 'Remote Assessment' visit, site staff will contact the subject by telephone to obtain information regarding adverse events and concomitant therapies.
